{"article_id":"Xkpb9BjSrjVvBgDX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Supporters of US President Donald Trump have turned on him","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after he was yet again denied funding for a border wall .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Late on Wednesday , the US Congress approved a spending bill","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to keep federal agencies open until February .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The Republican president was foiled in the Senate by his own party ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"which refused to grant him any of the $ 5bn","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"( £4bn )","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"he wants for a US-Mexico wall .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Two years on , Mr Trump has been unable to deliver on the central campaign pledge","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that electrified his rallies .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Congress faces a Friday midnight deadline","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"for averting a partial shutdown of the federal government .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Failing to agree a longer-term spending plan ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"the Senate has only been able to approve a seven-week extension of funds .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The House of Representatives is expected to act on the legislation later this week .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"President Trump told Republicans on Thursday afternoon","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"he would not approve any deal","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that denies him wall funding ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"according to House Speaker Paul Ryan .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"He later described it as a `` sacred obligation '' .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"`` I look forward to signing a bill","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that fulfils our fundamental duty to the American people , ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the president said on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Mr Trump has repeatedly suggested in the past","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"he will reject budget bills","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that include no money for his project ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"only to sign such measures","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"once they reach his desk .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"But fears of a government shutdown over the wall have set markets on edge .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"On Thursday the Dow fell by 2 %","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"- over 400 points -","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to a 14-month low ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"according to US media .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Members of the ultra-conservative House of Representatives Freedom Caucus were up in arms over the apparent retreat .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"North Carolina congressman Mark Meadows , a key Trump supporter , said :","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"`` He","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"[ Trump ]","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"campaigned on the wall . `","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"` It was the centre of his campaign .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"The American people 's patience is running out . ''","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"He called on the president to veto the bill","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and renegotiate .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Ohio congressman Jim Jordan noted in exasperation","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that it will only get more difficult next month","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"once Democrats take over the House .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"`` Let me get this straight , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Mr Jordan tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"`` Our chances","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"of getting the Wall","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"will be better in February","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"when Nancy Pelosi is Speaker","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"than now","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"when we have the majority ?","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Mr Trump 's champions in the media are also upset by his failure","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"to seal the deal .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Breitbart News called it a `` cave '' .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"The Drudge Report used the headline , `` Trump in Retreat '' .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Radio host Rush Limbaugh said","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"the president is going to `` get less than nothing '' .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Right-wing columnist Ann Coulter","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"- author of In Trump We Trust -","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"recently predicted","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"he will not be re-elected .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"`` Without a wall ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"he will only be remembered as a small cartoon figure","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"who briefly inflamed and amused the rabble , ''","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"she wrote .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Fox News host Laura Ingraham also posted a critical tweet .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders said on Thursday","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that Mr Trump is weighing his options .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"`` At this moment , the president does not want to go further","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"without border security ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"which includes steel slats or a wall , ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"she said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Despite enjoying two years of a congressional majority ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"Mr Trump was always unlikely to reach the 60 votes","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that funding for his wall would need in the Senate ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"where his party only currently has 51 seats .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"And some Republican lawmakers have baulked at the cost of such a barrier ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"expressing reluctance","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"to divert funding from other budgets , such as the military .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"While the wall debate continues ,","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"the Department of Homeland Security announced","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"that migrants","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"who illegally enter the US","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"- including asylum seekers -","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"will have to wait in Mexico","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"for their cases to be heard .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"The Mexican government has said","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"it will offer migrants work visas and protections","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"while they await asylum proceedings ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"according to the US Department of State .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"The advocacy group Kids in Need of Defense called the move `` unconscionable '' ,","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"that many families are fleeing violence .","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"Meanwhile , some Trump supporters have decided to take matters into their own hands ,","depth":4},{"id":96,"text":"launching a $ 1bn online fundraiser for the wall .","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"The GoFundMe has amassed more than $ 7m in three days .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"Brian Kolfage , the Iraq War veteran behind the campaign , said","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"raising the money was achievable","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"if every Trump voter pledged $ 80 .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"`` This wo n't be easy ,","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"but it 's our duty as citizens , ''","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Mr Kolfage said .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"`` We can help President Trump make America safe again ! ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":185,"right":208,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":119,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":106,"right":118,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":113,"right":117,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":111,"right":112,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":107,"right":110,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"N